In order to play Anno 1404 on Proton, follow these steps.
Install DirectX WINEPREFIX=/home/&lt;user&gt;/.local/share/Steam/steamapps/compatdata/33350/pfx wine /home/&lt;user&gt;/.local/share/Steam/steamapps/common/Anno\ 1404/DirectX/DXSETUP.exe Edit Engine.ini file The content of the file
/home/&lt;user&gt;/.local/share/Steam/steamapps/common/Anno\ 1404/Engine.ini &lt;InitFile&gt; &lt;DirectXVersion&gt;9&lt;/DirectXVersion&gt; &lt;UbiSurveyTime&gt;-1&lt;/UbiSurveyTime&gt; &lt;UbiSurveyTimeStatus&gt;2&lt;/UbiSurveyTimeStatus&gt; &lt;/InitFile&gt;

Install Dropbox using NixOS in your preferred way.
At the top of your i3wm configuration file add
exec dropbox &amp;
